query_result.query:
select * from (
select
    (select "PersonID" from members_mk_individual where mk_individual_id = mk_id) "PersonID",
    --knesset "כנסת", 
    --(select name from members_factions where id = faction_id) "מפלגה",
    sum(total_sessions) "ישיבות מליאה שהתקיימו בהן הצבעות", 
    sum(voted_sessions) "ישיבות מליאה שהחכ הצביע בהן",
    100.0 * sum(voted_sessions) / sum(total_sessions) "אחוז נוכחות"
from people_plenum_session_voters_stats
where
    knesset = (SELECT MAX("KnessetNum") FROM knesset_kns_knessetdates WHERE "IsCurrent")
group by knesset, faction_id, mk_id
order by "אחוז נוכחות" desc
) a
where "ישיבות מליאה שהתקיימו בהן הצבעות" > 1
